data.description: 55+ Gated. Resort Style Living. Prepaid Solar Panels. Rarely Available Model. Open Concept. 2 Bedrooms Plus a Den that could easily be a 3rd Bedroom or Anything You would like it to be. Extended Garage for Larger Trucks or Toys. Chef's Kitchen -  Upgraded Cabinets, Stainless Steel Appliances, Tiled Backsplash. Breakfast Area with Plenty of Space for a Table. Huge Granite Island Open to Great Room Overlooking The Entertainers Oasis Backyard with Rolling Wall of Glass. Pebble Stone Covered Patio, Built in BBQ. Enjoy a Morning Coffee on The Second Pebble Stone Patio off the Primary Suite. Primary Suite with Double Sinks, Upgraded Tiled Shower and Large Walk In Closet. Separate Guest Suite with Tub and Shower.  Dining Area can Accommodate a Large Table. Pebble Stone Driveway and Walk Way to the Front Door with a Custom Security Door. Fabulous Clubhouse with 2 Pools, Spa, Gym, Tennis/Pickleball, Putting Green, Dog Park, Social Calendar, Bocce Ball, BasketBall, Billiards and the list goes on
